This repo gives some examples of client applications to the JRC eSpecies services which are available at the following url:

https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//API.xml

The following client applications are included:

canvasTest.html	https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//canvasTest.html
Used to try out the various overlay operations with the HTML5 Canvas

charisma.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//charisma.html
Charismatic species gallery that shows the 'charisma' of species by taxonomic group based on the number of Flickr images for the species.

geeClient.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//geeClient.html
Google Earth Engine demonstration client used to show the integration of Google Earth Engine images related to a protected area.

index.html	https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//index.html
Simple page that loads range maps, protected areas, richness maps and species lists

landcover.html	https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//landcover.html
Uses the HTML5 canvas element to show different land cover types in the browser (not in IE<9)

landcoverValidator.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//landcoverValidator.html
Web client for spectral classification of land cover classes and method detection using Google Earth Engine.

overlay.html	https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//overlay.html
Uses the HTML5 canvas element to overlap different images in the browser (not in IE<9)

richness.html	https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//richness.html
Uses the HTML5 canvas element to show species richness and allow you to set the threshold in the browser (not in IE<9)

speciesValidator.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//speciesValidator.html
Demonstration web interface for updating species lists for protected areas based on the intersection of the WDPA and the IUCN Red List of Threatened Species.

tourism.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//tourism.html
Web mapping application that shows the tourism potential for protected areas in Africa based on their total charisma.

tourismGlobal.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//tourismGlobal.html
Web mapping application that shows the tourism potential for protected areas globally based on their total charisma.

validateSites.html https://andrewcottam.github.io/web-apps/eSpecies-Client-Demo//validateSites.html
Simple web tool for the rapid validation of pixels classified using Google Earth Engine.


